  "stem": "<p>Rectangle <em><math alttext=\"italic ABCD\"><mtext mathvariant=\"italic\">ABCD</mtext></math></em><em>&nbsp;</em>is similar to rectangle <em><math alttext=\"italic EFGH\"><mtext mathvariant=\"italic\">EFGH</mtext></math></em>. The area of rectangle <em><math alttext=\"italic ABCD\"><mtext mathvariant=\"italic\">ABCD</mtext></math> </em>is <math alttext=\"648\"><mn>648</mn>\n</math> square inches, and the area of rectangle <em><math alttext=\"italic EFGH\"><mtext mathvariant=\"italic\">EFGH</mtext></math> </em>is <math alttext=\"72\"><mn>72</mn>\n</math> square inches. The length of the longest side of rectangle <em><math alttext=\"italic ABCD\"><mtext mathvariant=\"italic\">ABCD</mtext></math> </em>is <math alttext=\"36\"><mn>36</mn>\n</math> inches. What is the length, in inches, of the longest side of rectangle <em><math alttext=\"italic EFGH\"><mtext mathvariant=\"italic\">EFGH</mtext></math></em>?</p>",
